Variable.Name: DRDINT
Variable.Description: Indicates whether the sample person has intake data for one or two days.

Variable.Name: DBQ095Z
Variable.Description: What type of salt {do you/does SP} usually add to {your/his/her/SP's} food at the table? Would you say . . .

Variable.Name: DR1STY
Variable.Description: Did {you/SP} add any salt to {your/her/his} food at the table yesterday? Salt includes ordinary or seasoned salt, lite salt, or a salt substitute.

Variable.Name: DRQSDIET
Variable.Description: Are you currently on any kind of diet, either to lose weight or for some other health-related reason?

Variable.Name: DR1TNUMF
Variable.Description: Total number of foods/beverages reported in the individual foods file

Variable.Name: DR1TWS
Variable.Description: When you drink tap water, what is the main source of the tap water? Is the city water supply (community water supply); a well or rain cistern; a spring; or something else?

Variable.Name: DRD340
Variable.Description: Please look at this list of shellfish. During the past 30 days did you eat any types of shellfish listed on this card? Include any foods that had shellfish in them such as sandwiches, soups, or salads.

Variable.Name: DRD360
Variable.Description: Please look at this list of fish. During the past 30 days did you eat any types of fish listed on this card? Include any foods that had fish in them such as sandwiches, soups, or salads.
